          "returnType": "Asset<TiledMap>",
          "description": "Annotation descriptor for the parsed Tiled source map, for Assets.from({...}) / loader.get(...) / loader.load(...) (asset-system v2 §5). This is the advanced parsed-source token; prefer the runtime TileMap (TileMap.of('world.tmj') or a bare 'world.tmj') for rendering. Use for dynamic paths or per-asset options — e.g. an explicit TiledLoadOptions.format hint for a .json path."
        }
